{"tid":2005344,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"美心集團疑大裁員逾100人 員工陸續返總部接「大信封」","createTime":"2020-05-07T04:59:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-07T05:37:36.000Z","uid":5195,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"9bfd512eb1865242673800112a2a2e8d3a48b660","tid":2005344,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T04:59:17.000Z","msg":"去年美心集團創辦人太子女伍淑清接受官媒訪問時，回應反送中運動稱，會「放棄」香港年輕人。正當香港年輕人從不怕遭人「放棄」之際，《蘋果》接獲讀者報料，指美心集團今日要「放棄」員工。據了解，約有100名員工被召見，今日到長沙灣美心總部接信，相信與裁員有關。記者接觸到數名員工，他們均承認收到指示前來接「大信封」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/20200507/AJ6J3ANIKSX5FXPVBXJYMJP544/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200507%2FAJ6J3ANIKSX5FXPVBXJYMJP544%2F&d=w9JnFmhD9tlFtzSpwKDBdTUBvjVF43IiJLn9vI4Fxnk%3D&h=88b715a7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200507%2FAJ6J3ANIKSX5FXPVBXJYMJP544%2F&h=835f6ed5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/20200507/AJ6J3ANIKSX5FXPVBXJYMJP544/</a>"},{"pid":"24f3748719117e9a46c9abf84c28508fc3f65e41","tid":2005344,"uid":61161,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T04:59:43.000Z","msg":"沉默的大多數呢？"},{"pid":"3475f81e772392124635fe13cbe5faa6035426c5","tid":2005344,"uid":2772,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T05:00:19.000Z","msg":"員工咪年青人<br />\n伍閪婆又贏"},{"pid":"5b43c191892b4d3c8515a65c1dee5f7a92dfb82c","tid":2005344,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T05:00:27.000Z","msg":"依家唔止放棄年輕人"},{"pid":"cc428f632adb187e76397bf4493ddd65c546a2da","tid":2005344,"uid":2837,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T05:00:39.000Z","msg":"員工被放棄了"},{"pid":"aec51b410f8f8515b4b70715231a324221c3dbf4","tid":2005344,"uid":245033,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T05:02:02.000Z","msg":"要放棄員工了"},{"pid":"6f9432fe79